  "texts": [
    "The U-Net was utilized to identify the primary area covering the text core known as X-height.",
    "Subsequently, a modified Run Length Smoothing Algorithm (RLSA) in combination with topological structural analysis was applied to detect entire lines.",
    "The X-heights identified by U-Net and the extracted foreground pixels by RLSA were then merged.",
    "Finally, ascenders and descenders were identified to pinpoint the ultimate text lines.",
